task.summary: Default task
Added JodaTime, search system
Fixed segfault on setting item property values directly.
Persist parent/child for corpses
More fixes to death system
Search site fixes
Fix food/thirst tracking
Fix experience calculation and granting
Fix for duplicate corpses on mod load.
Dialog system
Remove hard coded value for Skill requirement item property

Dialog system: Page switching Locations: Save on area enter, not on client leave (it's unreliable) Disease system: Only display message when infection is actually removed. Inventory system: Decrease the number of system items by 1. Feats: Add CustomFeat enumeration, remove hard coded reference to reload feat. Hunger system: Double the delay between hunger loss cycles.
Allow item uses to execute java classes on activation. Stubbed out rest menu.
More work on the conversation API, added support for color tokens on header.
Convert calls to NWObject.getObjectId() to hex.
Change level up message to floating text. Spawn system will now fire for DMs.
Boot players who aren't authorized DMs with a message.
Call different script which handles DM authorization checks
Fixes to disease zombification
Menu system framework
Change conversation method
Allocate SP Conversation: Upgrade selection + header display
Allocate SP Conversation: Skill upgrade purchasing
Added STR, DEX, CON, INT, WIS, CHA upgrade categories. Added skill checks to inventory system item limit method
Navigation options for allocate SP conversation
Key item menu
Split rest menu out into separate conversation classes
Outfit saving/loading
Outfit loading: Copy colors too
Increase max dialog responses to 12.
Portrait changing menu system
Head changing menu
Hide upgrade option if player reached max upgrades

Add "SetUp" method to all conversations. This should be used for building your conversations. The Initialize method should be used for manipulating response options and header texts. In addition, the "Disable PVP Protection" option has been set up in the rest menu.
Add/remove CD keys menu
Player CD key validation checks
Key item checks for displaying area maps, odds and ends
Migrate armor system to java
Migrate zombie AI scripts to java
Remove call to record PC counts
Public persistent storage
Reorganize location of placeable scripts
Pull loot tables from database and distribute them to search sites randomly based on weight.
Display "MAX" when no more skill upgrades can be purchased. Fix bug where default combat system would be used if PVP protection was on
Fix shotgun targeting issues.
Fix zombie respawn issue
Combat system: replace "assign" clear all action calls with "delay" calls.
Fix modifying skills/ability scores on upgrade purchase
Get max HP by level in progression system, not total max.
PC migration system, replaced setting response text in dialog system with custom tokens. Fixed issue where inventory system would not remove effects properly. Initializaiton of PCs sets NWN XP to 0.
